## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for nation.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers nation-aware visibility,
jurisdiction-aware display,
belonging-aware output,
policy-bearing runtime surfaces,
and bounded failure rendering.

## current_view_state
Runtime-visible nation state must distinguish:
- active nation
- restricted nation
- transformed nation
- historical nation
- dissolved nation

## validation_rules
- nation identity must resolve
- jurisdictional scope must resolve
- belonging scope must resolve
- policy scope must be valid
- cross-nation scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid nation identity
- invalid jurisdiction scope
- invalid belonging scope
- invalid cross-nation path
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish nation resolution,
jurisdiction validation,
policy-bearing state,
cross-nation denial,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- jurisdiction-aware runtime is explicit
- nation state rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
